 <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-black text-brandBlue uppercase italic tracking-tighter mb-4 text-center">Why <span class="text-brandOrange">TFT Display</span> for Your Brand</h2>
 <p class="text-center text-slate-500 text-sm max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">Premium positioning, higher margins, and a built-in unboxing moment. TFT-equipped power banks are the easiest upgrade path from commodity to flagship.</p>

 <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
 <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
 <h3 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase mb-3 text-sm">Premium Retail Positioning</h3>
 <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">MSRP $39-79 vs $15-25 for plain-shell models. The TFT screen and aluminum-glass build justify a flagship price point on Amazon, Apple Accessories shelves, and DTC stores.</p>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
 <h3 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase mb-3 text-sm">Corporate Gifting Appeal</h3>
 <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Tech-forward design and visible-utility stats screen make it a "wow" gift for executive presents, employee onboarding kits, and high-value client thank-yous.</p>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
 <h3 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase mb-3 text-sm">Unboxing Goes Social</h3>
 <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">The illuminated TFT screen photographs and films beautifully. TikTok, Instagram Reels, and YouTube unboxing shorts get organic engagement plain power banks never see.</p>
 </div>
 <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
 <h3 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase mb-3 text-sm">Real-Time Data Builds Trust</h3>
 <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Visible wattage and battery percentage prove the product is delivering rated performance. Reduces "is it actually fast charging?" complaints and warranty returns.</p>
