 </div>
 <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm">
 <h3 class="font-black text-brandBlue uppercase mb-3 text-sm">Qi2 Future-Proofs Your SKU</h3>
 <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Qi2 magnetic 15W wireless is the new baseline expected by iPhone 15+ and Galaxy S24+ users. Shipping a Qi2-certified product extends product lifecycle by 2-3 years.</p>
